{"title":"【C语言】找出3个数当中的最大值，并输出最大值","uid":"357ceba4bb7760cc0590dc559c62f0c7","slug":"【C语言】找出3个数当中的最大值，并输出最大值","date":"2021-11-29T02:38:17.000Z","updated":"2021-11-29T09:58:09.370Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/【C语言】找出3个数当中的最大值，并输出最大值.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/bj1.jpg","content":"<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">提示</p>\n<p>注意审题，如需要遍历的话，首先想到的是for循环</p>\n</div>\n<h1 id=\"实现原理\"><a href=\"#实现原理\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实现原理\"></a>实现原理</h1><p>1、首先要定义一个主函数main（）函数，因为主函数是程序的入口，没有入口，程序便无法正常运行。一般我们开始写程序的时候，都要先引入头文件和编写主函数，具体代码格式如下：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">#include&lt;stdio.h&gt;\n\nint main() &#123;\n\n\treturn 0;\n&#125;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong>此处的主函数主要用来获取值和输出值，具体的算法在maxvalue（）中实现</p>\n<p>2、其次就是定义一个maxvalue（）函数，用于判断三个数的最大值。此处定义的是一个有参函数</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">int maxvalue(int x,int y,int z) &#123;\n\n&#125;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong>此处的x,y,z分别代表三个数的变量名</p>\n<p>3、然后就是定义一个max变量，做为一个中间量来判断三个数的大小</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">int maxvalue(int x,int y,int z) &#123;\n\tint max;\n\tmax &#x3D; x;\n\tif (y &gt; max) &#123;\n\t\tmax &#x3D; y;\n\t&#125;\n\telse if (z &gt; max) &#123;\n\t\tmax &#x3D; z;\n\t&#125;\n\treturn max;\n&#125;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong>最后一定要记得返回max的值</p>\n<p>4、下一步就是编写main函数里的值的获取和输出</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">int main() &#123;\n\tint maxvalue(int x, int y, int z);\n\tint a, b, c, d;\n\tprintf(&quot;please input the value:&quot;);\n\tscanf_s(&quot;%d,%d,%d&quot;,&amp;a,&amp;b,&amp;c);\n\td &#x3D; maxvalue(a, b, c);\n\tprintf(&quot;the max is: %d&quot;,d);\n\treturn 0;\n&#125;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong><br>1、首先引用maxvalue（）函数，可写可不写；<br><br>2、其次定义a,b,c,d。其中a,b,c三个变量作为获取键盘上的值的变量名；<br><br>3、然后就是利用scanf（）函数来获取输入的值；<br><br>4、最后让d引用maxvalue（）函数来作为最大值输出<br></p>\n<h1 id=\"整体源码\"><a href=\"#整体源码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"整体源码\"></a>整体源码</h1><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">#include&lt;stdio.h&gt;\n\nint maxvalue(int x,int y,int z) &#123;\n\tint max;\n\tmax &#x3D; x;\n\tif (y &gt; max) &#123;\n\t\tmax &#x3D; y;\n\t&#125;\n\telse if (z &gt; max) &#123;\n\t\tmax &#x3D; z;\n\t&#125;\n\treturn max;\n&#125;\n\n\nint main() &#123;\n\tint maxvalue(int x, int y, int z);\n\tint a, b, c, d;\n\tprintf(&quot;please input the value:&quot;);\n\tscanf_s(&quot;%d,%d,%d&quot;,&amp;a,&amp;b,&amp;c);\n\td &#x3D; maxvalue(a, b, c);\n\tprintf(&quot;the max is: %d&quot;,d);\n\treturn 0;\n&#125;\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h1 id=\"实现结果\"><a href=\"#实现结果\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实现结果\"></a>实现结果</h1>  <img src=\"/img/max-from-three.png\" alt=\"some_text\">\n  \n  \n<div class=\"custom-quote danger\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M19.76 5.23C15.84 5.23 12 2 12 2C12 2 8.15996 5.23 4.23996 5.23C4.23996 5.23 1.86996 16.99 12 22C22.13 16.99 19.76 5.23 19.76 5.23Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 16H12\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">特别注意</p>\n<ul>\n<li>for循环的基本格式<ul>\n<li>初始化</li>\n<li>范围</li>\n<li>自增or自减</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>函数的调用    </li>\n</ul>\n\n</div>\n","feature":true,"text":" 提示 注意审题，如需要遍历的话，首先想到的是for循环 实现原理1、首先要定义一个主函数main（）函数，因为主函数是程序的入口，没有入口，程序便无法正常运行。一般我们开始写程序的时候，都要先引入头文件和编写主函数，具体代码格式如下： #include&lt;stdio.h&g...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.5k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"C语言练习","slug":"C语言练习","count":1,"path":"api/categories/C语言练习.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"C语言","slug":"C语言","count":1,"path":"api/tags/C语言.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86\"><span class=\"toc-text\">实现原理</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E6%BA%90%E7%A0%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">整体源码</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">实现结果</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Alion","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"少不习算法，老大掉头发","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"csdn":{"icon":"/img/csdn.png","link":"https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_43697439?spm=1000.2115.3001.5343"},"bilibili":{"icon":"/img/bilibili.png","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/339370258/article"},"github":{"icon":"/img/github.png","link":"https://github.com/Ai-Kevin"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"我的第三篇博客","uid":"3b323b55bdec257c038b644d7d7df594","slug":"我的第三篇博客","date":"2022-06-03T17:58:36.000Z","updated":"2022-06-03T18:34:15.858Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/我的第三篇博客.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/bj2.png","text":"这是我的第三篇博客 ","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":10,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Newcomer","slug":"Newcomer","count":7,"path":"api/categories/Newcomer.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Learn","slug":"Learn","count":6,"path"